{"type":"message","id":"fd6fa55f","parentId":"0ec38065","timestamp":"2026-03-25T23:47:38.193Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户现在说新闻早报的飞书文档是空的，要重新生成。首先我需要先读取那个飞书文档的内容确认是不是真的空的，对吧？首先得用feishu_doc的read操作，先拿到doc_token，从链接里看是ZkEWdZaXto3HL9xMjDac6CgCnBh对吧？对，飞书文档的token是docx后面那串。所以首先调用feishu_doc的read动作，参数是doc_token=\"ZkEWdZaXto3HL9xMjDac6CgCnBh\"，先看看文档内容是不是真的空的，然后再处理重新生成的事。\n哦不对，用户说空的，那可能是之前写的时候出问题了。那首先第一步先读取文档确认情况，然后再重新生成内容写进去。对吧？所以先调用feishu_doc的read工具，参数是action=\"read\"，doc_token=\"ZkEWdZaXto3HL9xMjDac6CgCnBh\"。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_kldrfp0r41b0qqeunny6qz43","name":"feishu_doc","arguments":{"action":"read","doc_token":"ZkEWdZaXto3HL9xMjDac6CgCnBh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":17041,"output":532,"cacheRead":7992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25565,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774482452197,"responseId":"021774482453596289ee8f5cd43d8cc040debd1abd108ae19e3c2"}}
