{"type":"message","id":"e3466b6a","parentId":"b9b1eba9","timestamp":"2026-03-25T23:49:07.418Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n太好了，文档已经成功写入了。现在需要告诉用户结果：文档已经重新生成完成，包含了所有要求的板块，链接还是原来的那个，让用户查看。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 飞书文档已重新生成完成！\n已完整填充所有板块内容：西安天气、伊朗局势、半导体新闻、乐鑫股票分析、国内国际新闻、股票基金推荐\n文档链接：[https://feishu.cn/docx/ZkEWdZaXto3HL9xMjDac6CgCnBh](https://feishu.cn/docx/ZkEWdZaXto3HL9xMjDac6CgCnBh)\n您可以点击链接查看完整内容。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":19055,"output":190,"cacheRead":36664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55909,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774482539581,"responseId":"0217744825408513d5a4ab7abe2b5478e0e510bcd83c12c64152c"}}
