{"type":"message","id":"1d146f16","parentId":"0bfda72b","timestamp":"2026-03-26T12:11:23.768Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户现在需要安装whisper，首先我得回忆一下whisper的安装方法，首先它是OpenAI的开源项目，需要Python环境，还有ffmpeg依赖对吧？首先先检查有没有Python和pip，然后安装whisper，还要装ffmpeg。首先先执行命令看看Python版本，之前知道用户的Python路径是C:\\Python314\\python.exe对吧？先执行命令安装whisper，用pip install openai-whisper，然后还要装ffmpeg，Windows的话可以用winget安装，或者提示用户如果没有winget的话怎么装。对了，还要验证安装是否成功，装完之后跑个whisper --version看看。首先先执行安装命令吧。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_mthqtwtlbo1d8haqipbbwnwp","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"C:\\Python314\\python.exe -m pip install openai-whisper -i https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-llm-chudian-site","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-pro","usage":{"input":61855,"output":373,"cacheRead":5944,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68172,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774527073341,"responseId":"0217745270737082b482879bf9ba508fa4c5c25749ab55936c1f9"}}
